# Job Portal Module — Walkthrough

## What Was Built

A complete Job Portal module for the ERP system — **13 new files, 1656 lines**.

## Architecture

```mermaid
graph TD
    A["Admin: /admin/jobs"] -->|CRUD| B["API: /api/admin/jobs"]
    A -->|"View apps/refs"| C["API: .../applications"]
    A -->|"View referrals"| D["API: .../referrals"]
    E["Student: /student/jobs"] -->|"List + eligibility"| F["API: /api/student/jobs"]
    E -->|"Apply"| G["API: .../apply"]
    E -->|"Refer"| H["API: .../refer"]
    F --> I["checkEligibility.ts"]
    G --> I
    I -->|"Checks"| J["Program, Grad Year, 10th/12th %"]
```

