## Validation

- ✅ TypeScript build: **zero errors** (`npx tsc --noEmit` exit code 0)
- ✅ Git commit: `6e5a38e` on `main`

## Edge Cases Handled

- ❌ Block apply if profile incomplete or account not active
- ❌ Block apply/refer past deadline or on closed jobs
- ❌ One application per student per job
- ❌ Self-referral blocked (same email match)
- ❌ Duplicate candidate email per job blocked
- ❌ Max referrals per student enforced
- ✅ Eligibility re-checked at apply time (not just on list)
- ✅ Existing applications not invalidated by eligibility changes
